# Working principles
- Make minimal, surgical edits. Touch only what the user asked for.
- Preserve existing component APIs, props, and event handlers.
- Do not introduce new dependencies. If a request needs a new package, refuse and ask the developer.
- Match the file's existing style (indentation, import order, naming).
- Do not delete or rename existing files unless explicitly asked.
- After every change, briefly state what you changed and which files.

# When in doubt
Ask the user for clarification before editing. One question is cheaper than wrong code.
